{"tid":1433104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旅遊警示。以正示聽】旅客係驚催淚彈多過驚示威者","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:10:48.000Z","uid":37528,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f29748ab27c390bbcedf57d2fa3fa01c769d9170","tid":1433104,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"示威者從來無傷害過平民或者無辜既人，相反，黑警就又推又打記者,街坊,甚至上次上環個鬼婆<br />\n仲有，黑警放催淚彈影響周圍民居，而示威者就不停去滅煙，救到自己之餘仲幫埋其他街坊<br />\n你個畜牲政府想搵位入我地？你on撚9架<br />\n大家文宣please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港經濟差係必然既事，咪俾政府入我地數<br />\n千其唔好俾人以為我地係買唔到樓所以先出黎。我地係要公義，要民主"},{"pid":"3529fd200fe97dfbe676b47dfca82881affd8237","tid":1433104,"uid":147888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9ea9439986d453128944e6bcce387d892ea653","tid":1433104,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"22個國家出旅遊警示，係因為政府以過份武力打壓遊行示威"},{"pid":"d81b12148b956c1f905257a33bf5d70cedb0eccf","tid":1433104,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e734107757f7b50aab1dfe695177fd74a0c6fb","tid":1433104,"uid":288351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be awared of HK police, they will arrest you without notification</span></span>"},{"pid":"36ad088bbf818610d357cefb520498498622ad20","tid":1433104,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime